com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.utils

Class FileUtils.CheckFileReadPermissionTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<File,Void,Boolean>
      • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.utils.FileUtils.CheckFileReadPermissionTask
  • Enclosing class:
    FileUtils

    public static class FileUtils.CheckFileReadPermissionTask
extends AsyncTask<File,Void,Boolean>
    Task checking whether app's process can read a file.

    The callback reference is strongly kept throughout the process, so it needs to be wrapped in a weak reference or released on the client side if necessary.
